description:
I can’t help but add a personal note to this match….After jumping into the Live Tag Team match-up last week and having Izamar pin me in such inescapable holds that could barely breathe, let alone move, it gives me extreme pleasure to watch her get her ass kicked all over the mat by a ROOKIE!!! Make sure not to miss the upcoming Tag Team Tuesdays to see who wins!!!
Mistress Kara may be new, but she may also be our new champion! Watch out Ariel, you have some fierce competition this year!!
title: "La Diabla" gets her ass Kicked by a ROOKIE!!!!
